{
  "stem": "24195.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So what he did is he got so despondent that he-- and despaired that he committed suicide on Christmas Day, I believe, 1933.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that devastated, of course, his, his wife and the two-- my two cousins, their two daughters.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they went-- they immediately-- they made-- they acted what my father probably should have done.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They went and-- went and immigrated to Switzerland immediately after that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they [LAUGHS] were able to, probably, to transfer most of their money to the Swiss banks.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they lived there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So that was this part of the, you know, the history in-- pre-war history.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I did not really feel any discrimination in, in grade school because--",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--like I said--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In public school, no, no, no, no, no.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, there was-- you know, I didn't feel any discrimination because [SIGHS] there were-- people were too young.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the teachers were not-- you were just-- you know, that was before the severe prosecution of the Jews really started.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So that--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it's about from 1933 to 1938, '39, just almost up to the beginning of the war, not quite.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think I started high school in 1938.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was after Kristallnacht.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that's when, of course, I had to-- I was already registered as a half-Jew, a half-Aryan person.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, you-- that was automatically.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, you had to-- you had to fill out every time-- well, as you entered school, there was a questionnaire that you had, an application form to school, which listed that question.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that's where you had to declare yourself.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, right, Aryan or non, yes or no.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that's-- and then, then if you say no, you're either a Jew or, in my case, a half-Jew.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And you have to spell that out.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
